	  /* Components/Utilities */
	- make a backup copy of the page.html.twig file (> page.html.twig.bak1)
	- create/ populate the page.html.twig with new suggestion for layout and regions (example file page.html.twig)
	- font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
