2. Setup the new regions in uit_theme.info.yml (se example file)
regions:
  header_left: Header Left Region
  header_center: Header Center Region
  header_right: Header Right Region
  highlighted: Highlighted Region
  sidebar_first: Sidebar First Region
  content: Content Region
  sidebar_second: Sidebar Second Region
  footer_left: Footer Left Region
  footer_center: Footer Center Region
  footer_right: Footer Right Region
3. Make a backup of the region.html.twig > region.html.twig.bak1
	In this file setup the correct class output for the region containers:
	> region|clean_class ~ '-region' (NB. use example-file)
